<p>There are two types of volume. A female volume and persistent volume. Ephemeral volume has a lifetime that is coupled to the pot Meaning that when a pot is terminated then. data store in the volume is lost as well On the other hand, persistent volume has its lifetime decoupled from the pot You can control the Data persist Or they say the volume life cycle completely different from the pot You had decide when you destroy The volume and therefore Controlled life cycle of the data</p>
